direction: right

User -> WebApp: Login/Manage Devices
User -> DesktopApp: Initiate/Host Session

RemoteDeskSystem: "RemoteDesk System" {
  WebApp: "Web Application (Next.js)" {
    WebUI: "Web UI (React)"
    WebAPIClient: "Web API Client"
  }

  DesktopApp: "Desktop Application (Electron)" {
    DesktopUI: "Desktop UI (React)"
    WebRTCClient: "WebRTC Client"
    ScreenCapture: "Screen Capture"
    InputHandler: "Input Handler"
  }

  BackendAPI: "Backend API (Node.js)" {
    AuthService: "Auth Service"
    DeviceService: "Device Service"
    SessionService: "Session Service"
    SocketIOServer: "Socket.IO Server"
  }

  DataLayer: "Data Layer" {
    PostgreSQL: "PostgreSQL DB"
    PrismaORM: "Prisma ORM"
  }

  ExternalServices: "External Services" {
    TURNServer: "TURN/STUN Server"
  }

  WebApp.WebUI <-> WebApp.WebAPIClient: API Calls
  WebApp.WebAPIClient <-> BackendAPI.AuthService: REST (Auth)
  WebApp.WebAPIClient <-> BackendAPI.DeviceService: REST (Devices)
  WebApp.WebAPIClient <-> BackendAPI.SessionService: REST (Sessions)

  DesktopApp.DesktopUI <-> BackendAPI.AuthService: REST (Auth)
  DesktopApp.DesktopUI <-> BackendAPI.DeviceService: REST (Device Reg)
  DesktopApp.DesktopUI <-> BackendAPI.SessionService: REST (Session Mgmt)

  DesktopApp.DesktopUI <-> SocketIOServer: Signaling (Socket.IO)
  WebApp.WebUI <-> SocketIOServer: Signaling (Socket.IO)

  DesktopApp.WebRTCClient <-> TURNServer: WebRTC (Media/Data)

  BackendAPI.AuthService <-> PrismaORM: Data Access
  BackendAPI.DeviceService <-> PrismaORM: Data Access
  BackendAPI.SessionService <-> PrismaORM: Data Access
  PrismaORM <-> PostgreSQL: SQL

  DesktopApp.ScreenCapture -> DesktopApp.WebRTCClient: Video Stream
  DesktopApp.InputHandler -> DesktopApp.WebRTCClient: Input Events (Data Channel)
}

User -> WebApp.WebUI: Access Dashboard
User -> DesktopApp.DesktopUI: Install/Run App

DesktopApp.DesktopUI -> DesktopApp.ScreenCapture: Request Screen Share
DesktopApp.DesktopUI -> DesktopApp.InputHandler: Capture Input

DesktopApp.WebRTCClient -> DesktopApp.DesktopUI: Remote Video/Control
